{"tid":112446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［羅馬教廷都出事］羅馬街頭現海報 批教宗方濟各：你的慈悲那裡去了？","createTime":"2017-02-08T07:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T10:57:44.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ddca5690acbed5361c9b3c2456755a6def70d9","tid":112446,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"【羅馬街頭出現批評教宗海報】<br />\n【請為教會和教宗祈禱】<br />\n<br />\n（綜合外電報導／公教報譯）二月四日早上，羅馬街頭出現一些批評教宗方濟各的海報，海報印有教宗方濟各相片和「你的慈悲那裡去了？」字句，又提及近期的馬爾他騎士團事件。<br />\n　海報沒有下款或任何團體的標記，市政府則以「非法宣傳品」紙張遮蓋原有海報，因為上述海報未有事先申請或繳納稅項。<br />\n　教廷方面未有回應事件。<br />\n　路透社引述耶穌會公教文明編輯Antonio Spadaro神父在社交媒體推特中指出：教宗做出了對的事，所以激怒了不少人。<br />\n　近期馬爾他騎士團出現人事爭拗，教宗派員介入，觸發馬爾他騎士團團長法拉．瑪竇．菲廷（Fra' Matthew Festing）不滿和辭職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pope-knights-posters-idUSKBN15J0V0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-pope-knights-posters-idUSKBN15J0V0&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=295cfbed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-pope-knights-posters-idUSKBN15J0V0&h=861bdfcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pope-knights-posters-idUSKBN15J0V0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cruxnow.com/vatican/2017/02/04/rome-wakes-find-city-full-anti-pope-francis-posters/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcruxnow.com%2Fvatican%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2Frome-wakes-find-city-full-anti-pope-francis-posters%2F&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=f1dac94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cruxnow.com/vatican/2017/02/04/rome-wakes-find-city-full-anti-pope-francis-posters/</a>"},{"pid":"bb3dd0c3d5017ea2a669014e8c86b7efa4e91772","tid":112446,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"質而我權力既通常都冇好下場"},{"pid":"6fe948a2d0c0ccbee63174e7978ec4f4ae465f4b","tid":112446,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,